- `transferOperator_inner_nonneg`: ‚ü®f, Tf‚ü© ‚â• 0
- `transferOperator_eigenvalues_pos`: all Œª·µ¢ > 0
- `transferOperator_ground_simple`: unique leading eigenvalue with strict gap
